PASS 3 — CROSS-MODAL REFERENCE (5x stable)
  Text → all other modalities
  All → text (back-references)
  Inter-modality (pass 3+)
  All edges registered in CrossModalIndex (Section B.7)
  State after: CrossLinked → Stable
